zm_pollution_v1

Polluted industrial area, with thick smoky atmosphere. 70 something spawnpoints for zombiemod servers. Been working on this map on and off since September last year, and finally it's ready. I haven't made a zombie mod map in years, so Im sure I'll end up having to release a 2nd version later. Let me know if improvements are needed.
